,"msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4525b340a9b516c5e4d205bcdb3416a7429340d","tid":1672181,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:48:21.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇優惠啊"},{"pid":"878ab41ff6a8bf7fcef0c4afa2e637583e1a5906","tid":1672181,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eeeb57caa8a492cbdb356ecb573d64ce43a659a7","tid":1672181,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T03:10:27.000Z","msg":"郁d就激嬲<br />\n郁d就唔理香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:48:30.000Z","msg":"想出四格漫畫"},{"pid":"33c8eb2cd0b6b6fbee16883865de5a88cfa06dcd","tid":1672181,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:48:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">中共斥巨資收賣西方<br />\n遊說集團統戰華盛頓</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=4668a5e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=2c76c686\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抗衡中國魔掌<br />\n組建香港既遊說團隊！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=e38d7691\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=77658ae9\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。</span>"},{"pid":"f03d45694c855969d05351be2a660bd75efd9d69","tid":1672181,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884d8862b34d7e1de96e0d462ff6e1dedf08de07","tid":1672181,"uid":59608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:49:52.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47cb18a5155fc5360991f89b5527e907d302f9d7","tid":1672181,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c386d8e384a63b6e2aaabf9bdf5cf0e5275d5b","tid":1672181,"uid":218659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:50:59.000Z","msg":"你唔知 唔想take依個risk"},{"pid":"41f19636573dd739e877ea6a35137bcfd3564d01","tid":1672181,"uid":265449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:51:32.000Z","msg":"最on9係以為條女想同你結婚"},{"pid":"1cf76e3c56b87818b742e7330e189687358d66ea","tid":1672181,"uid":165339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:57:18.000Z","msg":"條女根本唔支持你出嚟創業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448bc35af824f6c6f969f1a3b26563c4572ce0c5","tid":1672181,"uid":324892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:58:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d1ba9134d609d36b5f601c9998283c66f2f3a75","tid":1672181,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s